com.vaadin.addon.charts.client
Interface HighchartResources

All Superinterfaces:
com.google.gwt.resources.client.ClientBundle
public interface HighchartResources
extends com.google.gwt.resources.client.ClientBundle

Client bundle that contains the JavaScripts, etc required for Vaadin Charts.

Actual injection of these scripts is done by HighchartsScriptLoader, but to e.g. change script versions you can just replace this bundle with GWT deferred binding.
